There's a funny feature (looks like a bug)
in the classe
org.apache.tools.ant.taskdefs.optional.extension.ExtensionAdapter
in the method Extension toExtension()

I feel more confortable if someone swap the 'error' commented lines below (see 
the Extension constructor).

best regards

